title: Crysonic - Almost Everything Bundle
description:
Crysonic - Almost Everything Bundle 

- CRY'Q
- newB 2
- nXtasy 3.0
- SINDO 3.5
- SPECTRA C1
- SPECTRALIVE NXT 3.5
- SpectraPhy LE
- SPECTRAPHY 2.3HD
- SPECTRA'Q


Crysonic Three Extra Plugins

Crysonic Spectralive NXT 4.0
Crysonic TRANSILATE 1.0
SpectraC2

NOTE: Spectra C1 may not work on install. It did not for me and froze up my DAW (Ableton Live 8.3) and was it was disabled on restart. Use the .dll file in the Three Plugins folder instead for Specta C2. 


This collection was found on a Russian BT site. N
Find lots of cool stuff in those site but they are not the safest sites in the world but I seem to be having no issues as far as malware or viruses goes. Scanned on my end and all plugins running okay. Nice little collection I have not seen a nearly full collection for yet at the regular sites here. 

As always enjoy. And, please, if you make money with these plugins, remember, who cares. 

Uranium Willy
